snippet.textDisplay:
@ZobmieRules Well, I have to admit my tendency to never flee from fights and to avoid boarding because I think it's overpowered doesn't necessarily help my case, but I have been in situations where there's just no way I could've made it through. (Lots of beacons with nothing happening and thus not earning enough scrap being the most prevalent.)

On a side note, it always seems to me like the dodge-chance is rigged. Like, an enemy automated scout only needs 5% dodge and 70% of your shots will miss, guaranteed. You on the other hand will still take almost every shot even with 40%. Maybe it's negative confirmation bias, iunno.

That said I still love the game, having over 800 hours clocked in and gotten almost every achievement there is. <3

